{"title":"照亮","date":"2018-07-08T10:38:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 8, 2018","L":"07/08/2018","MM-DD":"07-08"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/12/iO8YBDmfgteGuRh.jpg","link":"2018/07/08/照亮","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.498Z","content":"<p>每粒尘埃<br>\n每颗星体<br>\n都默然地牵引</p>\n<p>缓缓转动<br>\n落满银河<br>\n在悬臂上斑驳闪耀</p>\n<p>渺如星火<br>\n微不足道<br>\n但灯<br>\n一盏便足以照亮一切</p>\n<p>烟花芳华瞬逝<br>\n青柏残留千古<br>\n撒一片阴凉</p>\n","prev":{"title":"枫","link":"2018/11/15/枫"},"next":{"title":"岩浆","link":"2018/05/30/岩浆"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2018/07/08/照亮/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"66 words in 1 min"}